snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Carnage Official Trailer - Available on iOS & Android
snippet.description:
Warhammer 40,000: Carnage is Available Now on iOS & Android!
Play the #1 Action-RPG set in the 40k universe now!
Get CARNAGE Now on the App Store: http://taps.io/LsGQ
OR Get It Now on the Google Play Store: http://taps.io/LsFg

This Official Trailer for CARNAGE is made 100% in-house by Roadhouse Interactive, with all cinematics using in-game assets, and Gameplay taken directly from the game. 

Jump into instant chaotic destruction as a legendary Space Marine. Pick your weapons and do untold damage as you run and gun through screaming hordes of ruthless enemies in this fast-moving action Side-Scroller. Armed with a Boltgun in one hand and Chainsword in the other, fight foul Orks and save the rage-filled planet Mithra. For the Emperor!

Warhammer 40,000: Carnage is a kick-ass action game built for anyone who gets extreme satisfaction from destroying hordes of Orks.

Official Warhammer 40,000: Carnage site: http://www.playcarnage.com
